\series default
)或
\series bold
方差-协方差矩阵(variance–covariance matrix)
\series default
，是一个平方
\begin_inset CommandInset href
LatexCommand href
name "矩阵"
target "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matrix_(mathematics)"
literal "false"

\end_inset

，给出给定
\begin_inset CommandInset href
LatexCommand href
name "随机向量"
target "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Random_vector"
